title: Math 218: Spring 2023
text:
Materials
There is no required textbook for this course.
You should have a fully-charged laptop, tablet with keyboard, or comparable device to every lecture and lab session.
You should also have R and RStudio installed on your machine. If you do not have either, please follow these instructions.
